Tyrael looked back when he heard Kaiser collapse. He then saw that
Dread was down too. He went over to her and took her in his arms. He
then turned to Destructor.

Tyrael: I guess our discussion will have to be delayed. Can you help
bring Kaiser back to the base? (He turned to Prometheus) As you can
see, we were the strongest. We could use your strength, however, and
that of your companion too. Thus, I welcome you in the ranks of the
Tripredacus. Can you fly?

into a
